snippet.title: Frakktus - Endless Music Arcade Trailer
snippet.description:
Frakktus is an endless rhythm music arcade game for mobile devices.
Play with a brain probe, destroy your Mental blocks from Mandalas of Truths. Raise your reaction, shake your deep feelings, increase awareness by color therapy and comprehend some new truths!

You can play with your favourite Music!

Developed in solo by Conferno.

:: Beta :: Release soon ::

Subscribe in socials and you will be First, who will know about the release date!
 
http://instagram.com/frakktus 

http://vk.com/frakktus_official

http://twitter.com/frakktus

http://facebook.com/frakktusgame 

Music by @Darkman007
